parameters:
Chinatsu: "To go north, we have to get through that construction
site."

Chinatsu: "Lately, it seems there have been cases of women being
abducted around here, so I'd rather not walk through deserted
places..."
01_優衣_何

Yui: (That must be the abduction case the officer was talking about.
If I remember correctly, a man named Chikunai Iwao is the
ringleader...)
Yui: (So the incidents have been happening around this area...)
Let's slip through the construction site together!
It's dangerous, so we should take a detour
一緒に工事現場を抜けましょう！
01_優衣_デフォルトA
Yui: "Let's go through the construction site together."

Yui: "Actually, I'm also feeling uneasy... But it'll be reassuring if
we're together."

Chinatsu: "That sounds good. Even if the culprit is there, we won't
have to worry about being targeted if we're together..."
Chinatsu: "It's reassuring to be with someone else, so let's do that!"
Yui: "Then, shall we go?"
危険ですので遠回りした方が…
01_優衣_戦闘えっ

Yui: "There could be unforeseen circumstances, so it might be better
to take a detour..."
Chinatsu: "You're right. It's a hassle, but maybe we should do that."
Tetsuta: "That construction over there never seems to finish."

Tetsuta: "They're supposed to be building a factory after demolishing
the park, but it's been half a year since they started and it's still
in that state."

Tetsuta: "It seems Saionji Pharmaceuticals is involved, but lately, I
haven't heard any good rumors about them."

Tetsuta: "In the past, there was a park there... It was a place of
rest for the local residents..."
Chinatsu: "Well, that was anticlimactic. I was totally fine."

Chinatsu: "I didn't feel like the culprit was hiding anywhere. I
wonder if there really is a kidnapping case happening."
01_優衣_デフォルトA
Yui: "It's a relief that nothing happened."
Yui: "It was an unnecessary worry, wasn't it?"
Chinatsu: "Really! I worried for nothing. Hahaha!"
Chinatsu: "Well then, I'll be off!"
Yui: "(It seems it was just me. I definitely felt someone's gaze...)"

Yui: "(Even without transforming into Pony-Celeste, my senses have
become sharpened.)"

Yui: "(Perhaps the repeated battles with Zaida-G have made the holy
power assimilate into my body.)"

Yui: "(If that gaze was indeed from the culprit, then it's certain
that the kidnapping case is happening here.)"
Yui: "(How shall I catch the perpetrator, I wonder?)"
01_優衣_デフォルトA

Yui: "(That's it! If I'm alone, the culprit might show themselves. A
decoy strategy sounds like a brilliant idea♪)"
Yui: "(Alright, let's give it a try!)"
Yui has unlocked \c[12]Fast Travel\c[0]!

Yuzuru: "Hmm, Building No. 2 is nice, but I guess Building No. 1 is
better..."

Yuzuru: "No, Building No. 3 is also good... It's tough to decide where
to settle."

Yuzuru: "Sanko-Po is a pretty popular apartment around here because
it's cheap and comfortable to live in."
Fumiaki: "Whoops, I'm not a suspicious person, you know."

Fumiaki: "Lately, this area has been quite dangerous, huh? Just
wearing goggles during the day gets me mistaken for some weirdo, it's
troubling."

Fumiaki: "Don't you get this fashion? Oh era, hurry up and catch up to
me! Just kidding!"
Shigeki: "In the past, you could even catch sweetfish around here."

Shigeki: "We used to attach string and bait to tree branches and catch
a lot of them."

Shigeki: "Now, with one development after another, the river has been
ruined, the fish are gone, and it's become quite lonely..."
